## 30. SpecialFood con hilo seguro (fix thread-safety)

```java
// EN SpecialFood.java — versión corregida
public class SpecialFood extends Food {
    private volatile boolean active = true; // volatile para visibilidad entre hilos
    public static final int MAX_MILLISECONDS = 10000;
    public static final int MIN_MILLISECONDS = 3000;
    private SpecialFoodRemover foodRemover;

    public SpecialFood(Snake snake, SpecialFoodRemover foodRemover) {
        super(snake);
        this.foodRemover = foodRemover;
        int visibleMs = (int)(Math.random()*(MAX_MILLISECONDS-MIN_MILLISECONDS)+MIN_MILLISECONDS);

        new Thread(() -> {
            try {
                Thread.sleep(visibleMs);
                if (active) {
                    // Ejecutar en el hilo de Swing (thread-safe)
                    javax.swing.SwingUtilities.invokeLater(() -> {
                        foodRemover.removeSpecialFood();
                    });
                }
            } catch (InterruptedException e) {
                Thread.currentThread().interrupt();
            }
        }).start();
    }

    public void deactivate() { active = false; }

    @Override
    public void paint(java.awt.Graphics g, int w, int h) {
        Util.drawSquare(g, getRow(), getCol(), java.awt.Color.magenta, w, h);
    }
}

// EN Board.tick() — desactivar si se come antes de que expire:
if (snake.eats(food)) {
    if (food instanceof SpecialFood) {
        ((SpecialFood) food).deactivate(); // ← evita que el hilo la elimine después
        snake.incrementNodesToGrow(3);
        incrementer.incrementScore(20);
    }
    // ...
}
```

